{"tid":1802772,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【2019亞姐】晚裝裙棄打底 nude bra大媽底褲盡入眼簾","createTime":"2019-12-29T17:18:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T07:30:15.000Z","uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"626f986830737a74b8638d5820afa0688763dd63","tid":1802772,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T17:18:15.000Z","msg":"甫開場，16位候選佳麗以薄紗晚裝上陣，而最吸睛的，相信就是1號楊采薇、11號丁雪怡及13號徐麗麗，皆因她們的晚裝中門大開，而當中又以楊采薇最為突出。至於香港代表15號羅思雅，未知她的晚裝是否有下滑跡象，只見她在轉身時抽了一下衣服。首輪是透視晚裝，質地非常薄，部份佳麗出場時nude bra、大媽底褲都現形。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191229/large/1577624662_df56.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191229%2Flarge%2F1577624662_df56.jpg&h=b8a456ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n15號羅思雅谷胸上陣。"},{"pid":"1b13203ed172a2b03e94b1cd4b2817f4360b4544","tid":1802772,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T17:18:33.000Z","msg":"司儀陳啟泰訪問坐在台下評判之一的郭可盈，提到兩人在94年合作《刑事偵緝檔案》時飾演情侶，問到對方見完16位佳麗後有甚麼感覺，郭可盈說：「每個都充滿自信，大家都來頭不少，攞過獎項，我自己亦有心水。」而陳啟泰之後再問郭可盈會否復出拍戲？她笑說：「你等我問一問屋企嗰兩個老細先。」當陳啟泰跟郭可盈表示很多人都想她復出拍劇，而郭可盈就以「一言為定」來回覆對方。"},{"pid":"1af804ae0415070ffbc960b99b12eb47b2c6c9e6","tid":1802772,"uid":44730,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T17:18:49.000Z","msg":"問答環節講香港文化，2號台灣佳麗翁子涵抽到咖哩魚蛋，陳啟泰用廣東話問：「你係咪食得魚蛋多，所以身材好？」翁子涵最初聽唔明，最後她妙答：「如果沒吃過就好像沒有去過香港，正如沒有我就不算是選美。」"},{"pid":"f672e6be0c6b7062e61214ae8fe5abb7a139b59d","tid":1802772,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T17:18:53.000Z","msg":"幾正"},{"pid":"51887823226c7df82231746bb599f7f2cf191386","tid":1802772,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T17:19:05.000Z","msg":"3號葉采昕抽到電視台，她讚香港電視台多姿多采多元化，又數出多個巨星如周潤發、梁朝偉及即將上任副總裁的林文龍，不過她列舉的人都是無綫出身。"},{"pid":"9a16386b9587d30216a430e4f812d79160c74ccf","tid":1802772,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T17:19:21.000Z","msg":"香港代表9號范莎莎抽到太平山頂，由於她讀過旅遊管理，題目如度身訂造，她如維基百科一樣大講歷史，又說：「我今晚好似太平山頂一樣，麻雀雖小，但係東方之珠。」聽到觀眾𢱑頭，不知她想表達甚麼。同是香港代表的15號羅思雅就抽到菠蘿包，她表示：「菠蘿包外脆內軟、思想前衛、勇往直前，就好似現代女性一樣，菠蘿包就係我喇，為咗夢想勇往直前，私底下係賢內助，希望我能夠名振國際。」"},{"pid":"21d60b6f71a690a52ee0548b831b5e50923c719f","tid":1802772,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T17:19:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>德國聯署有三份  呢家仲有一份未達標 <span style=\"color: red;\">最後兩日</span><br />\n<br />\n德國減少對中國和其他非民主國家的依賴<br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_09%2F_01%2FPetition_98731.html&d=OJrKX0dn%2BAqYJaSYBqJK9yHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=a491541d\" target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"11d68052a1d99ac50bea41cc96636ad4980cbecd","tid":1802772,"uid":7854,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T17:19:38.000Z","msg":"圖呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0401cd12a8e506991cee43427924ef6665ac060c","tid":1802772,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T17:19:59.000Z","msg":"腳趾姐都有睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb94dc446fef348363d3fd1f6f9701f1beb9b43c","tid":1802772,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T17:20:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191229/large/1577624664_02e5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191229%2Flarge%2F1577624664_02e5.jpg&h=9c044771&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n13號徐麗麗（左）的大媽底褲現形。"},{"pid":"00e656d37aac1196e44c6e94dbdbc1e64fd34743","tid":1802772,"uid":322732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T17:24:02.000Z","msg":"唔怪得郭可盈要去現場睇實老公<br />\n好多女妖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b538369ac665d5786c64c8d0e8236e96a117f25f","tid":1802772,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0401cd12a8e506991cee43427924ef6665ac060c","tid":1802772,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T17:19:59.000Z","msg":"腳趾姐都有睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T17:24:47.000Z","msg":"<em>仆你個街！亞視嚟嘅喂</em>.jpg <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/LEMfr09.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FLEMfr09.gif&h=68991de0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f48209b401a60da21306c065d79f1cb94daa523d","tid":1802772,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T17:25:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2019/12/1577627872_lN-1280w.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2019%2F12%2F1577627872_lN-1280w.JPG&h=1153dfa0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n金剛離開無綫機會，有不少工作與他接洽。<br />\n<br />\n上年亞姐選完冇人知，未知是否怕重蹈覆轍，今年《2019亞洲小姐競選》在大埔總台舉行，到場的有麥翠嫻﹑陳庭威﹑陳靖允、劉錫賢、羅霖﹑肥媽﹑羅敏莊﹑彭家麗胞弟彭皓鋒及已離巢無綫的李天翔等，更邀請任賢齊、欣宜當表演嘉賓。主持方面除了有陳啟泰外，還邀請金剛擔任。他笑言很怕是最後一次，而經理人表示已收齊了酬勞。"},{"pid":"603364c20bc66ee86347baa1a701ff244470f0d8","tid":1802772,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T17:25:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2019/12/1577627885_1C-1280w.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2019%2F12%2F1577627885_1C-1280w.JPG&h=02d3e1e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另一表演嘉賓欣宜表示欣宜第一次踏足亞視，感覺很特別，大讚綵排時配樂製作亦很用心。欣宜笑言日前抽空打扮，因為好蠢以及慳家，在家中自行漂眉來配合金髮造型，但分心做其他事而不幸灼傷而「眉毛穿窿」。"},{"pid":"1da1aea8e04f66a4544f5ecc2db986f181f740ee","tid":1802772,"uid":132174,"like":14,"dislike"